make better products
We are leading the future of compounded plastic materials.  We excel in creating unique solutions for our customers inelectrical, agriculture and automotive, healthcare andhousewares, and everything in between.  At Citadel, we offer unparalleled breadth and depth of knowledge, technology, and operational agility, expanding the boundaries of materials and technologies. 




our brands

